      <textAnnotation id="sid-2DAC9B17-DC37-4143-9999-4C2DCF9E5B4C" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bottom="false" left="false" ref="text_name" right="false" top="true" valign="bottom" x="32.0" y="-9.0"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>OneSource Tax Apps</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-962DA4BF-D85D-4CA4-A3D4-7A525947E31D" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bottom="false" left="false" ref="text_name" right="false" top="true" valign="bottom" x="32.0" y="-9.0"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>OneSource Tax Apps</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-EFDEC2F5-7F43-43A0-BDB0-0696815A4142" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Assessment Based on to-be process (e.g. production started or not , order in cancellation window or not) and determine prices
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-DEA90186-8CAC-4D93-958D-32E5F4171D3D" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Manual registration of pushout/cancelation request from Customer to CBA/Marketing Team
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-E4D42F1A-AE05-4721-8784-6268132057F5" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1. Manual Assessment by CBA/Marketing Team on feasibility of request from customer
2. CBA will immediately put manufacturing put on hold even before assessment if request if for cancellation. </text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-7E592789-48A1-48DD-A0FE-5968095DF3AC" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>BY ESP / OP</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-0663C8CB-B041-4F52-B0B8-055ECEC0497D" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Refer Manufacturing E2E-74 flow and Architecture Diagram to understand detailed level interfacing
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-1FAD4B2C-E3E1-4F41-A97E-7BDDA273E081" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Cascading feed to prioritize others order by freeing existing capacity
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-434FDC4E-DBFE-4237-8BD4-701428AD5357" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel ref="text_name" valign="middle" x="29.0" y="49.0"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>CBA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-DB2DD6B2-C910-41B1-951A-7FB000D045E2" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Check for Cancellation Window
And BU approval if NCNR order
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-5F1354A7-5C6C-43E9-A2BA-4A5C4C71466C" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Push-Out RDD
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-9E4026C1-F6AD-46B6-85D5-43BC8FD502A2" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Dr. Account Receivables
Cr. Sales/Penalty /Others Acc
Dr. Taxes (if applicable)
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-7399C9F2-3A7E-441A-8BEA-98EC0EF0E765" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Feed of confirmed sales order to communicate rescheduling and prioritization of other production orders
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-E551D939-72F6-44CC-A795-1AB86E38807A" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Dr. Account Receivables
Cr. Sales
Dr. Taxes (if applicable)
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-CDBE8869-BCE3-4F3E-89DF-29A4B7B328AB" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text> DR: Customer (Account Receivable}
CR:  Sales Revenue
Cr . Taxes (if applicable)
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-DB0B65E2-D80E-4E23-8EF9-374F317B04A9" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text> DR: Customer (Account Receivable}
CR:  Sales Revenue
Cr . Taxes (if applicable)
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-64F2DE63-D38B-41B5-B5F9-0E11FEDC15ED" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text> DR: Customer (Accounts Receivable)
CR:  Customer (Account Receivable)
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-53E4B0CF-116F-45F3-9D72-68364349B3AC" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>DR: Bank Clearing Account
CR:  Customer (Accounts Receivable)
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
   </process>
